WEBVTT

00:01:57.969 --> 00:02:00.191
biroz hazil ohangini beradi.

00:02:00.191 --> 00:02:03.655
Bu og'zaki kinoya va sarkazm.

00:02:03.655 --> 00:02:06.450
"Sen qobiliyatli sportsmensan" deb 
olimpiadachiga aytilsa,

00:02:06.450 --> 00:02:09.334
bu to'g'ri eshitiladi, va bu yerda 
kinoya yo'q.

00:02:09.334 --> 00:02:11.619
Lekin aynan shu ibora darsda kitobi va 
qurollari

00:02:11.619 --> 00:02:14.420
har joyda yoyilib yotgan o'quvchiga 
aytilsa,

00:02:14.420 --> 00:02:18.137
bu qo'polroq, va shuningdek kinoyali.

00:02:18.137 --> 00:02:21.421
Chunki siz aynan nazarda tutgan gapingizni
aytmadingiz.

00:02:21.421 --> 00:02:23.550
Bu og'zaki kinoya.

00:02:23.550 --> 00:02:25.436
Nazarda tutganingizning teskarisini

00:02:25.436 --> 00:02:27.323
gapirdingiz.
Undan tashqari, bu orqali

00:02:27.323 --> 00:02:29.303
siz bu inson ustidan kulishga

00:02:29.303 --> 00:02:31.849
qaror qildingiz, 
bu nafaqat kinoya bo'ldi,